    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>Kid,

I take it you're aware of the Overlord's latest decree. If not, let me give it to you straight. Now's a bad time to be an Archon in the Tiers. Since most likely I'll be the one to cut you down, I thought I'd first explain - it's not my choice. 

But if it was, I would still choose to kill you. See you soon,

- [url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url], Archon of Shadows and Court Blade</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>[url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url],

If I am to die by your hand, I would prefer it be in battle, face to face (or would that be face to shadow).

Regardless, at the risk of depriving you the thrill of a good ambush, I would ask that we meet in person, as peers - drawing blades openly - if it that is what it is to come to. On the reverse of this parchment, I've mapped for you a location in the wilderness. Let us meet and settle things there.

I'll provide you two days to scout the location in advance should you require.

Hope to see you there,
- [Player Name]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>Arrange a meeting.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>Say something cordial.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
