    <Entry>
      <ID>15</ID>
      <DefaultText>Kid,

Since it was you that asked, sure. Why not? I could wait for the Adjudicator's official order, but this seems much more interesting. 

Here're my conditions - we meet alone and we meet with our blades drawn. And no crying when I carve your eyes out.

I've already scouted the clearing you indicated in your note. Arrive when you like, and I'll make my presence known.

Remember - no tears. No begging.

- Mark</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>16</ID>
      <DefaultText>Kid,

If I haven't said it before, I'll say it now. I'm going to enjoy killing you. Can't wait for the execution order. I'll be anticipating your arrival at the Court.

Don't snuff the lights,
- [url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url], Archon of Shadows and Court Blade</DefaultText>
