    <Entry>
      <ID>18</ID>
      <DefaultText>[url=lore:Missive_BledenMark]Kid,

I have to say, you never did play by the rules. But now you've ceased even pretending to serve the Overlord, to which the Adjudicator is not amused. Unfortunately, the chaos you have wrought in casting an unsanctioned Edict hinders our campaign in the Tiers and weakens belief in the Overlord. You will at once, come to our Court, largely, to offer penance for threatening Kyros' rule of the Tiers. But do not fear,[/url] [url=glossary:tunon]Tunon[/url] [url=lore:Missive_BledenMark]will preside without bias, and order me to execute a sentence that is fair in the eyes of the law, and only if you are found guilty at the trial. But I can promise you this - If you want to live, it would be unwise to ignore his summons. If and when you first wish to speak with the other Archons to beg mercy, we will not prevent you but we would encourage you to refrain. At our behest, [/url][url=glossary:the voices of nerat]the Voices of Nerat[/url] [url=lore:Missive_BledenMark]and[/url] [url=glossary:graven ashe]Graven Ashe[/url][url=lore:Missive_BledenMark], are also weighing the consequence of your bald-faced rebellion.[/url] 

-[url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url], [url=lore:Missive_BledenMark]Archon of Shadows and Court Blade[/url]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>19</ID>
      <DefaultText>Kid,

If I haven't said it before, I'll say it now. I'm going to enjoy killing you. Can't wait for the execution order. We'll settle this now. Meet me in a spot of shade in depths of Ashweald. That is, if you're not afraid of being swallowed by the dark. 

Your executioner,
- [url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url], Archon of Shadows and Court Blade</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>20</ID>
      <DefaultText>Kid,

If I haven't said it before, I'll say it now. I'm going to enjoy killing you. And while I'd love to carve your heart out and feed it to the darkness in a remote spot in a shaded weald, unlike you, I'm not dumb enough to act on a whim. Can't wait for the Adjudicator's execution order. I'll be anticipating your arrival at the Court.

Don't snuff the lights,
- [url=glossary:bleden mark]Bleden Mark[/url], Archon of Shadows and Court Blade</DefaultText>
